Betty Jane Rhodes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_Jane_Rhodes 0 Betty Jane Rhodes (April 21, 1921 – December 27, 2011) was an American actress and singer, most active in film during the late 1930s and the World War II era. She was also known as Jane Rhodes. Betty_Jane_Rhodes ( April_21_,_1921 – December_27_,_2011 ) was an_American_actress_and_singer , most_active in film during the_late_1930s and the_World_War_II_era .
